\
\'93No, Misha, no. If that\'92s all, you\'92ve reassured me. It won\'92t come to\
that.\'94\
\
\'93But why are you trembling? Let me tell you; he may be honest, our Mitya\
(he is stupid, but honest), but he\'92s\'97a sensualist. That\'92s the very\
definition and inner essence of him. It\'92s your father has handed him on\
