\
\'93I understand that,\'94 Alyosha jerked out suddenly.\
\
\'93Really? Well, I dare say you do understand, since you blurt it out at the\
first word,\'94 said Rakitin, malignantly. \'93That escaped you unawares, and\
the confession\'92s the more precious. So it\'92s a familiar subject; you\'92ve\
thought about it already, about sensuality, I mean! Oh, you virgin soul!\
You\'92re a quiet one, Alyosha, you\'92re a saint, I know, but the devil only\
knows what you\'92ve thought about, and what you know already! You are pure,\
but you\'92ve been down into the depths.... I\'92ve been watching you a long\
