is lawful. (And by the way, do you remember how your brother Mitya cried\
out: \'91I will remember!\'92) An attractive theory for scoundrels!\'97(I\'92m being\
abusive, that\'92s stupid.) Not for scoundrels, but for pedantic _poseurs_,\
