about so much?\'94\
\
\'93Of course he isn\'92t.\'94\
\
\'93And as for the ideas he may be hatching, the Russian peasant, generally\
speaking, needs thrashing. That I\'92ve always maintained. Our peasants are\
swindlers, and don\'92t deserve to be pitied, and it\'92s a good thing they\'92re\
