\
\'93And for the last time there is not.\'94\
\
\'93Who is laughing at mankind, Ivan?\'94\
\
\'93It must be the devil,\'94 said Ivan, smiling.\
\
\'93And the devil? Does he exist?\'94\
\
\'93No, there\'92s no devil either.\'94\
\
\'93It\'92s a pity. Damn it all, what wouldn\'92t I do to the man who first\
