in what.\'92 \'94\
\
\'93Really?\'94\
\
\'93He really did. But I respect him. There\'92s something of Mephistopheles\
about him, or rather of \'91The hero of our time\'92 ... Arbenin, or what\'92s his\
name?... You see, he\'92s a sensualist. He\'92s such a sensualist that I should\
be afraid for my daughter or my wife if she went to confess to him. You\
