\
\'93What, he stole it?\'94\
\
\'93He brought him the money as a man he could trust, saying, \'91Take care of\
it for me, friend, there\'92ll be a police search at my place to\uc0\u8208 morrow.\'92 And\
he kept it. \'91You have given it to the Church,\'92 he declared. I said to him:\
