\'93Alyosha,\'94 he whispered apprehensively, \'93where\'92s Ivan?\'94\
\
\'93In the yard. He\'92s got a headache. He\'92s on the watch.\'94\
\
\'93Give me that looking\uc0\u8208 glass. It stands over there. Give it me.\'94\
