\
\'93No, father, and it wouldn\'92t be suitable, it wouldn\'92t be right at all.\'94\
\
\'93Where was he sending you just now? He shouted \'91Go\'92 as he ran away.\'94\
\
\'93To Katerina Ivanovna.\'94\
\
\'93For money? To ask her for money?\'94\
\
\'93No. Not for money.\'94\
\
\'93He\'92s no money; not a farthing. I\'92ll settle down for the night, and think\
