\
\'93Yes, yes!\'94 cried Alyosha warmly. \'93I believe that is it.\'94\
\
\'93And, if so, he\'92s not altogether lost. I can still save him. Stay! Did he\
not tell you anything about money\'97about three thousand roubles?\'94\
\
\'93He did speak about it, and it\'92s that more than anything that\'92s crushing\
