do you know about the money?\'94 he added, and suddenly broke off.\
\
\'93I\'92ve known of it a long time; I telegraphed to Moscow to inquire, and\
heard long ago that the money had not arrived. He hadn\'92t sent the money,\
but I said nothing. Last week I learnt that he was still in need of money.\
