Father Zossima\'97\'94\
\
\'93Four days, what nonsense! Listen. Did you laugh at me very much?\'94\
\
\'93I didn\'92t laugh at all.\'94\
\
\'93Why not?\'94\
\
\'93Because I believed all you said.\'94\
\
\'93You are insulting me!\'94\
\
\'93Not at all. As soon as I read it, I thought that all that would come to\
