\
\'93To\uc0\u8208 morrow\'97to Moscow!\'94 her face was suddenly contorted; \'93but\'97but, dear me,\
how fortunate!\'94 she cried in a voice suddenly changed. In one instant\
there was no trace left of her tears. She underwent an instantaneous\
