\
Alyosha broke off and was silent.\
\
\'93You ... you ... you are a little religious idiot\'97that\'92s what you are!\'94\
Katerina Ivanovna snapped. Her face was white and her lips were moving\
with anger.\
\
Ivan suddenly laughed and got up. His hat was in his hand.\
\
\'93You are mistaken, my good Alyosha,\'94 he said, with an expression Alyosha\
had never seen in his face before\'97an expression of youthful sincerity and\
