\'91Well?\'92 said I. I saw his eyes flashing. \'91Father, how he treated you\
then!\'92 \'91It can\'92t be helped, Ilusha,\'92 I said. \'91Don\'92t forgive him, father,\
don\'92t forgive him! At school they say that he has paid you ten roubles for\
