don\'92t know. I only know that I, too, am a Karamazov.... Me a monk, a monk!\
Am I a monk, Lise? You said just now that I was.\'94\
\
\'93Yes, I did.\'94\
\
\'93And perhaps I don\'92t even believe in God.\'94\
\
\'93You don\'92t believe? What is the matter?\'94 said Lise quietly and gently. But\
Alyosha did not answer. There was something too mysterious, too subjective\
