\'93To be shot,\'94 murmured Alyosha, lifting his eyes to Ivan with a pale,\
twisted smile.\
\
\'93Bravo!\'94 cried Ivan, delighted. \'93If even you say so.... You\'92re a pretty\
monk! So there is a little devil sitting in your heart, Alyosha\
Karamazov!\'94\
