\'93Why are you trying me?\'94 Alyosha cried, with sudden distress. \'93Will you\
say what you mean at last?\'94\
\
\'93Of course, I will; that\'92s what I\'92ve been leading up to. You are dear to\
me, I don\'92t want to let you go, and I won\'92t give you up to your Zossima.\'94\
