\'93No, I can\'92t admit it. Brother,\'94 said Alyosha suddenly, with flashing\
eyes, \'93you said just now, is there a being in the whole world who would\
have the right to forgive and could forgive? But there is a Being and He\
can forgive everything, all and for all, because He gave His innocent\
