\
And she actually put the cord round his neck, and began arranging it. In\
extreme embarrassment, Mitya bent down and helped her, and at last he got\
it under his neck\uc0\u8208 tie and collar through his shirt to his chest.\
\
\'93Now you can set off,\'94 Madame Hohlakov pronounced, sitting down\
triumphantly in her place again.\
\
\'93Madam, I am so touched. I don\'92t know how to thank you, indeed ... for\
such kindness, but ... If only you knew how precious time is to me....\
That sum of money, for which I shall be indebted to your generosity....\
Oh, madam, since you are so kind, so touchingly generous to me,\'94 Mitya\
exclaimed impulsively, \'93then let me reveal to you ... though, of course,\
you\'92ve known it a long time ... that I love somebody here.... I have been\
false to Katya ... Katerina Ivanovna I should say.... Oh, I\'92ve behaved\
inhumanly, dishonorably to her, but I fell in love here with another woman\
