\
\'93But the money? The three thousand?\'94 Mitya exclaimed, awkwardly.\
\
\'93Oh, if you meant money, I haven\'92t any. I haven\'92t a penny, Dmitri\
Fyodorovitch. I\'92m quarreling with my steward about it, and I\'92ve just\
