\'93I don\'92t understand you!\'94\
\
\'93Am I drunk?\'94\
\
\'93Not drunk, but worse.\'94\
\
\'93I\'92m drunk in spirit, Pyotr Ilyitch, drunk in spirit! But that\'92s enough!\'94\
