\
\'93What are you giving it him for?\'94 cried Pyotr Ilyitch, irritably.\
\
\'93Yes, yes, yes, let me! I want to!\'94\
\
\'93E\'97ech!\'94\
\
Misha emptied the glass, bowed, and ran out.\
\
