As he said this, Mitya suddenly got up.\
\
\'93Dmitri Fyodorovitch, won\'92t you come now?\'94 called Andrey from the door of\
the shop.\
\
\'93Are you ready? We\'92ll come!\'94 Mitya started. \'93A few more last words\
