\
\'93Dmitri Fyodorovitch, dear good Dmitri Fyodorovitch, don\'92t harm my\
mistress. And it was I told you all about it.... And don\'92t murder him, he\
came first, he\'92s hers! He\'92ll marry Agrafena Alexandrovna now. That\'92s why\
