\
\'93He\'92s a fool, though he\'92s a good fellow,\'94 he muttered as he went. \'93I\'92ve\
heard of that officer, Grushenka\'92s former flame. Well, if he has turned\
up.... Ech, those pistols! Damn it all! I\'92m not his nurse! Let them do\
