\
\'93How do you mean?\'94\
\
\'93I don\'92t feel differently, but I wish I hadn\'92t hated him so.\'94\
\
\'93You feel penitent?\'94\
\
\'93No, not penitent, don\'92t write that. I\'92m not much good myself, I\'92m not\
