\
Chapter IV. The Second Ordeal\
\
\
\'93You don\'92t know how you encourage us, Dmitri Fyodorovitch, by your\
readiness to answer,\'94 said Nikolay Parfenovitch, with an animated air, and\
obvious satisfaction beaming in his very prominent, short\uc0\u8208 sighted, light\
