he cried, looking at them with a good\uc0\u8208 nature that was almost surprising.\
\'93It\'92s only Mitya Karamazov, you know, so you can overlook it. It would be\
inexcusable in a sensible man; but you can forgive it in Mitya. Ha ha!\'94\
