\
\'93Excuse me. How\'92s that? Why, when you were here a month ago you spent\
three thousand, not fifteen hundred, everybody knows that.\'94\
\
\'93Who knows it? Who counted the money? Did I let any one count it?\'94\
\
\'93Why, you told every one yourself that you\'92d spent exactly three\
thousand.\'94\
\
\'93It\'92s true, I did. I told the whole town so, and the whole town said so.\
