\
\'93It\'92s not the fifteen hundred that\'92s the disgrace, but that I put it apart\
from the rest of the three thousand,\'94 said Mitya firmly.\
\
\'93Why?\'94 smiled the prosecutor irritably. \'93What is there disgraceful, to\
