\
\'93The preliminary inquiry is not yet over,\'94 Nikolay Parfenovitch faltered,\
somewhat embarrassed. \'93We will continue it in the town, and I, for my\
part, of course, am ready to wish you all success ... in your defense....\
As a matter of fact, Dmitri Fyodorovitch, I\'92ve always been disposed to\
