\
\'93One must sniff round a bit first,\'94 he observed to Smurov.\
\
\'93Why ask him to come out?\'94 Smurov protested. \'93You go in; they will be\
awfully glad to see you. What\'92s the sense of making friends in the frost\
out here?\'94\
\
\'93I know why I want to see him out here in the frost,\'94 Kolya cut him short\
in the despotic tone he was fond of adopting with \'93small boys,\'94 and Smurov\
