\
\'93The classical languages, too ... they are simply madness, nothing more.\
You seem to disagree with me again, Karamazov?\'94\
\
\'93I don\'92t agree,\'94 said Alyosha, with a faint smile.\
\
\'93The study of the classics, if you ask my opinion, is simply a police\
