\
\'93That\'92s true,\'94 assented Smurov suddenly, in a ringing tone of conviction.\
He had listened attentively.\
\
\'93And yet he is first in Latin himself,\'94 cried one of the group of boys\
suddenly.\
\
\'93Yes, father, he says that and yet he is first in Latin,\'94 echoed Ilusha.\
\
\'93What of it?\'94 Kolya thought fit to defend himself, though the praise was\
very sweet to him. \'93I am fagging away at Latin because I have to, because\
