boys hurriedly took leave. Some of them promised to come again in the\
evening. Kolya called Perezvon and the dog jumped off the bed.\
\
\'93I won\'92t go away, I won\'92t go away,\'94 Kolya said hastily to Ilusha. \'93I\'92ll\
wait in the passage and come back when the doctor\'92s gone, I\'92ll come back\
