\
\'93What do you mean by mystic? Cure me of what?\'94 Alyosha was rather\
astonished.\
\
\'93Oh, God and all the rest of it.\'94\
\
\'93What, don\'92t you believe in God?\'94\
\
\'93Oh, I\'92ve nothing against God. Of course, God is only a hypothesis, but\
... I admit that He is needed ... for the order of the universe and all\
