\
Alyosha repeated all Grushenka had said to him that day. Mitya listened,\
made him repeat things, and seemed pleased.\
\
\'93Then she is not angry at my being jealous?\'94 he exclaimed. \'93She is a\
regular woman! \'91I\'92ve a fierce heart myself!\'92 Ah, I love such fierce\
hearts, though I can\'92t bear any one\'92s being jealous of me. I can\'92t endure\
it. We shall fight. But I shall love her, I shall love her infinitely.\
