you, you know, Alexey, because you are the only person who can understand\
this. There\'92s no one else. It\'92s folly, madness to others, all I\'92ve told\
you of the hymn. They\'92ll say I\'92m out of my mind or a fool. I am not out of\
my mind and I am not a fool. Ivan understands about the hymn, too. He\
understands, only he doesn\'92t answer\'97he doesn\'92t speak. He doesn\'92t believe\
in the hymn. Don\'92t speak, don\'92t speak. I see how you look! You have\
