\
\'93What did he lie on there?\'94\
\
\'93Well, I suppose there was something to lie on. You are not laughing?\'94\
\
\'93Bravo!\'94 cried Ivan, still with the same strange eagerness. Now he was\
listening with an unexpected curiosity. \'93Well, is he lying there now?\'94\
\
\'93That\'92s the point, that he isn\'92t. He lay there almost a thousand years and\
