the actor Gorbunov says.\'94\
\
\'93Well, did you get your nose pulled?\'94(8)\
\
\'93My dear fellow,\'94 observed the visitor sententiously, \'93it\'92s better to get\
off with your nose pulled than without a nose at all. As an afflicted\
marquis observed not long ago (he must have been treated by a specialist)\
