nose.\'92 \'94\
\
\'93Fool, how stupid!\'94 cried Ivan.\
\
\'93My dear friend, I only wanted to amuse you. But I swear that\'92s the\
genuine Jesuit casuistry and I swear that it all happened word for word as\
