\'93I repeat, moderate your expectations, don\'92t demand of me \'91everything\
great and noble\'92 and you\'92ll see how well we shall get on,\'94 said the\
gentleman impressively. \'93You are really angry with me for not having\
appeared to you in a red glow, with thunder and lightning, with scorched\
