\
\'93Open, open to him. There\'92s a snowstorm and he is your brother. _Monsieur\
sait\uc0\u8208 il le temps qu\'92il fait? C\'92est \'e0 ne pas mettre un chien dehors_.\'94\
\
The knocking continued. Ivan wanted to rush to the window, but something\
seemed to fetter his arms and legs. He strained every effort to break his\
