\
\'93Alyosha, I told you not to come,\'94 he cried fiercely to his brother. \'93In\
two words, what do you want? In two words, do you hear?\'94\
\
\'93An hour ago Smerdyakov hanged himself,\'94 Alyosha answered from the yard.\
\
\'93Come round to the steps, I\'92ll open at once,\'94 said Ivan, going to open the\
door to Alyosha.\
\
\
\
Chapter X. \'93It Was He Who Said That\'94\
\
\
Alyosha coming in told Ivan that a little over an hour ago Marya\
Kondratyevna had run to his rooms and informed him Smerdyakov had taken\
his own life. \'93I went in to clear away the samovar and he was hanging on a\
